title: Season 6 Victorious Ward Skin
body:
With the new client, when in champion select I noticed that the rank 3 season 6 victorious ward skin is displayed as the classic green ward.

New client is beautiful btw :D

replies.body:
Hiya Neato Mojito! 

Thanks for the report! Looks like we may have missed a few image assets when creating them for the new client (yay beta!) I'll see what we can do to get this resolved ASAP!
